name: Akeena Hinton
text: It's the best pizza around, having nice crust and plenty of cheese you'll be sure to eat more than one piece.

name: Tyler Olsen
text: Just received my order. Burnt and missing pasta and marinara dipping sauce. Tried calling and no one answered. What a rip off.

name: Chelsey Lipka
text: Since the new owners took over, it's been going down hill. I've had bad experiences every time. Most pizzas are never cooked all the way and usually doughy or soggy in the middle. Plus, none of the sales or deals are ever applicable in my area so it's the most expensive pizza in town.

name: Rissie Olsen
text: Ordered two dinner boxes. Pasta was missing from one box. The pizzas look AWFUL, burnt and cold. Also missing the marinara sauce for the breadsticks. Tried calling in to give them a chance to make it right and our calls were ignored for 20 minutes. Very disappointing and $80 down the drain (that $10 tip was not earned).

name: Scott Cummings
text: Worst pizza i have ever had in Rocksprings . It smelled like fish. And that was after the dude about ran me over in his pickup. This is the second time i have tried pizza hut. There won't  be a third.

name: Bob Dole
text: Pizza left delivery place over an hour ago, still hasnt shown up yet. They ignored calls when trying to call into the restaurant. This is ridiculous, and I had to pay and I havent gotten my food. So enjoy the extra 50 you crooks hope it keeps you warm in Hell
